FT  01 JUL 94 / Vaz protests at Abu Dhabi move
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Mr Keith Vaz, Labour MP for Leicester East, yesterday called on the Lord
Chancellor to investigate a petition made to the Legal Aid Board by the
solicitors to the Ruler of Abu Dhabi.
In an early day motion he criticised Simmons &amp; Simmons for writing a letter
